{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the [GERMAN] Strasse, it's like Caroline Street is really what it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this school was run by Jews, staffed by Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The children, many of whom went there of course, came off from observing-- mostly from observing homes, Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There really was no Conservative.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was Reform.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Reform was more Conservative, like Conservatism here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So most of them, many of them were Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had had Hebrew from the first year of school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And here I was-- 11 years old, 11 and 1/2 almost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had not had Hebrew, even though I was attending the temple instructions, I wasn't learning Hebrew there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And where was I going to start?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was like, you know, I had so many years that were lost to me as far as Hebrew was concerned.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was expected to keep up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What I did keep up was-- was the Hebrew songs we sang, which were what later became Israel, Palestinian, those kinds of songs that became very popular amongst young Jewish people, like and all that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so that I could keep up with.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew all of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I couldn't keep up with the Torah reading.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't keep up with anything like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so that put me in a bad situation right off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of the teachers there I was very unhappy with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, it was like going from the frying pan into the fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was some anti-Semitism to a certain kind of anti-Jewish-- anti-Reformed Jewish feeling, which is one-- I was also attending a Jewish day camp in the summer.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as somebody very succinctly put it at that time, you really don't belong to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you don't belong to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
